---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Philosophy | Wanbe" description="The story behind our minimalist and healthy living movement.">
    <section class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.4em] font-black text-gray-400 block mb-8">
            The Philosophy
        </span>

        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] mb-12 uppercase italic">
            Value, <br/> 
            <span class="text-gray-300">Not Stuff.</span>
        </h1>

        <div class="space-y-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-800">
            <p class="font-bold text-2xl tracking-tight text-black">
                Wanbe was born out of anxieties about an overly noisy world. We believe that your living space should be a place of healing, not a burden.
            </p>

            <p>
                Many people accumulate things for status, but forget the essence of comfort and well-being. Here, we curate a slower, more conscious, and more meaningful way of living.
            </p>

            <div class="py-8 border-y border-gray-100 my-12">
                <h3 class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest font-black mb-4">Our Core Pillars</h3>
                <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <li>
                        <span class="block font-black uppercase text-sm">01. Essentialism</span>
                        <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic leading-snug">Only keep what truly provides value.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="block font-black uppercase text-sm">02. Well-being</span>
                        <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 italic leading-snug">Design that supports air circulation and mental peace.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p>
                We're not just a decoration blog. We're a journal for those of you who want to build a healthy little "empire" amidst the chaos of the digital world.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-20 pt-10 border-t border-black">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter mb-4">Join the movement</p>
            <a href="/blog" class="text-3xl font-black tracking-tighter hover:text-gray-400 transition-colors uppercase italic">
                Read the Journal →
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>